<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-21-0378 </DOCNO><TEXT>Steps taken by various segments of the chemical industry of Romania toconsume less energy are described. The elimination of energy losses throughmaintenance of installations, the utilization of by-products, and themodernization of installations are all factors in the reduction of energyconsumption. Energy saving measures for the manufacture of ammonia, methanol,aluminum, carbides, caustic soda, and chlorine are briefly described.</TEXT></DOC>